The evidence with the title 'Fact check: obamacare's medicare cuts | time.com ' says Aug 16, 2012  ... Since the Romney-Ryan campaign is hammering the Obama-Biden ticket on the Affordable Care Act's $716 billion in cuts to Medicare, it seems useful to put this  ... Even with the ACA cuts, the CBO says the cost of Medicare is expected to grow from about $500 billion in 2012 to nearly $900 billion by 2022. 
